### 10. `background-attachment: fixed` — Scroll Jank on All Devices

**File:** [`globals.css`](file:///f:/PROJECTS/wayfindsolutions/src/app/globals.css#L102)

```css
body {
  background-image: linear-gradient(...);
  background-attachment: fixed; /* ← kills GPU compositing */
}
```

This forces the browser to repaint the full background on every scroll frame, dropping frames and causing stutter. Especially severe on mobile. Two-minute fix:

```css
body {
  background-image: linear-gradient(...);
  background-size: 48px 48px;
  /* remove background-attachment: fixed */
}
```

