## 🟡 MEDIUM SEVERITY ISSUES

### 11. Root Layout Makes a Live DB Call Per Worker Process

**File:** [`layout.tsx`](file:///f:/PROJECTS/wayfindsolutions/src/app/layout.tsx#L21-L26)

`unstable_cache` caches in-memory **per worker process**. On PM2 cluster with 4 workers, the first request to each worker hits Supabase. On free tier where the DB is slow, this adds latency to the first load on each worker restart.

**Fix:** Switch the layout to ISR. Since public pages will use `revalidate = 3600`, the layout data will also revalidate on the same cadence automatically.

