### 12. Supabase Free Tier in Tokyo — Geographic Latency

Your database is on `aws-0-ap-northeast-1` (Tokyo). If your users are in Pakistan or the Middle East, and Hostinger is in Europe/Asia, every DB query adds **80–200ms of network RTT** that can't be optimized away without moving regions.

**Mitigation:** ISR caching (Issue #2) is the only real fix — once pages are cached, the DB latency is paid only once per hour, not per visitor.

