## 🏁 Root Cause Summary

```
Supabase Free Tier (paused DB, Tokyo region, shared compute)
        +
force-dynamic on every page (no caching, hits DB on every visit)
        +
pool max:1 (serializes all parallel queries)
        +
Spline iframe (3–8s third-party WebGL load)
        =
A site that is fundamentally slow at every layer
```

**The fastest wins with zero cost:**
1. Set up a keepalive cron ping → stops the 10–30s cold start
2. Replace `force-dynamic` with ISR → public pages stop querying the DB on every visit
3. Change pool `max` to 3 → admin queries actually run in parallel
4. Defer the Spline iframe → hero loads instantly

These four changes take under 1 hour combined and will make the site feel dramatically faster.
